OL,3,CDog fouling complaints soar as fines
OL,4,Cissued plummet
OL,6,FThere are thousands of dog lovers
OL,7,Facross Northern Ireland and when out
OL,8,Fand about, most take responsibility
OL,9,Ffor cleaning up after their pets.
OL,11,FThose who fail to do so can face a
OL,12,Ffine of up to #200.
OL,14,FHowever, figures from local councils
OL,15,Fshow that complaints about dog fouling
OL,16,Fare rising but the number of penalties
OL,17,Fbeing issued has plummeted.
