OL,3,CDog fouling complaints soar as fines
OL,4,Cissued plummet
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's 11 councils have
OL,7,Freceived almost 16,000 complaints
OL,8,Fabout dog mess in the last five years,
OL,9,Fbut only 800 fixed penalty notices
OL,10,Fhave been issued during the same
OL,11,Fperiod.
OL,13,FData sourced by Compare NI also
OL,14,Freveals that the number of fines
OL,15,Fhanded out has dropped from 110 in
OL,16,F2023 to 57 in 2024.
