OL,3,CDog fouling complaints soar as fines
OL,4,Cissued plummet
OL,6,FBelfast City Council recorded the
OL,7,Fhighest number of complaints ` 4717
OL,8,Fsince 2019` but its 12 enforcement
OL,9,Fofficers issued just 54 fines in that
OL,10,Ftime.
OL,12,FArds and North Down had the second-
OL,13,Fhighest number of complaints (2,102)
OL,14,Fbut issued more fines than any other
OL,15,Fcouncil (171).
OL,17,FCauseway Coast and Glens, Fermanagh
OL,18,Fand Omagh and Antrim and Newtownabbey
OL,19,Fhave not handed out a single fixed
OL,20,Fpenalty notice for more than 18 months.
